"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/731275","Department for Exiting the European Union","false","2017-06-28","<p><strong>The Department for Exiting the European Union intends to publish its 2016-17 Annual Report and Accounts before the House rises for the summer recess.</strong></p>","Wycombe","Mr Steve Baker",,"2017-06-28T12:31:51.3Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/731275/answer","Biography information for Mr Steve Baker","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/731275/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/731275/answer",,,,,"203","Exiting the European Union","Exiting the European Union","2017-06-21","Department for Exiting the European Union: Annual Reports","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Exiting the European Union, when he plans to publish his Department's Annual Report and Accounts for 2016-17.","false","Biography information for Tom Brake","Carshalton and Wallington","Tom Brake","31"
